In a message dated 6/12/03 11:30:35 PM Central Daylight Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> hydras looked the computer that comfirmed that the visitor was 
> Maxima. He looked her and he was amazing that he saw. 

Entering through the doorway, as she strode towards him.

> 
> "Ahhhh, my dear Tigress, I love your new look"hissed the male
> 
> 
> 

Smirking as she marched up towards him. Then stopped just short of his 
throne. Saluting in the old Decepticon way, arm crossing over her breastplate. "It's 
far better than the previous form. At least, I can fly." 

Standing to attention. "I have many things to report," she went straight into 
it. Always duty & work before pleasure with her. For her duties were so 
rather appealing & fun for her. 

She went on to tell him about his 'training' sessions with Blackstorm & her 
accompanying her on 'patrol'. Then of the call on another continent from old 
Decepticons, which she & Blackstorm intercepted. Blackstorm had intercepted on 
known as Sideways. She proceeded to explain her mistrust in Sideways. As well 
explain of another leary one known as Hevn, who was constantly following 
Blackstorm. She had mentioned that they returned to this continent when they were 
side tracked near the Ark by more arrivals then the arrival by the Autobots & 
Maximals started a small standoff, in which she was shot down. Then lost for a 
spell, found by Azureblade & Scourge. 

She dare not mention however, that she had went to the Ark at the  beginning 
for personal reasons, let alone the lagoon that she 'found'. The Lagoon, she 
could take Hydras to as a surprize, she thought. 

"I don't likely trust this Hevn, who follows Blackstorm like a shadow. Nor do 
I care much for Sideways." Still standing there infront of him, erect like a 
soldier at attention. 

--part1_11.133b8883.2c1b3183_boundary
